emuInput.TitMainTitle: Dandy Duffers golf club members and guests, including Alma Speed Fox seated second from right; in rear: Betty Tibbs eleventh from left, Irving Johnson sixth from right, and Gerald Fox seventh from right, posed in Joyce Room at Flamingo Club
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline for image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 27, 1954, pg. 11, reads: "Dandy Duffers - A portion of the happy throng of Dandy Duffers, their wives or sweethearts and guests is shown reving [sic] it up at the Flamingo's Joyce Room last Sunday evening at the gala cocktail party.  The DDs are golfers who decided to entertain before the season really gets under way. - Harris Photo."
